Class DummyPOSTagger

      opennlp.ccg.parse.postagger.DummyPOSTagger

public class DummyPOSTagger
extends POSTagger

A "DummyPOSTagger" simply grabs the single POS tag in the Words themselves and puts them into a TaggedWord with a singleton list of probability 1.0 POS tags.
